{"cells":[{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"NQAGIlRMsget"},"source":["#Taller 3 - Metodos Computacionales\n","## Sofia Moscoso Ortiz\n","## 1015068640"]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["import numpy as np                     #librerias\n","import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n","import math as mt\n","import time"],"metadata":{"id":"Fywr7yfq0i8P"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"RI1CZ-hVsget"},"source":["#**1** En mecánica orbital, al resolver el problema de la fuerza central se hace necesario resolver la ecuación de Kepler. Esta es una ecuación trascendental que relaciona los parámetros orbitales de la trayectoria.\n","\n","*Kepler equation:* $M = E - \\epsilon \\sin E$\n","\n","donde $ M $ es la anomalía media, $ E $ la anomalía excéntrica y $ \\epsilon $ la excentricidad. La anomalía media se puede calcular con la expresión\n","\n","$$M = n\\ t = \\sqrt{ \\frac{GM_c}{a^3} } t$$\n","\n","donde $ n $ es el movimiento medio, $ G $ la constante gravitacional, $ M_c $ la masa del cuerpo central y $ a $ el eje semi-mayor. $ t $ es el tiempo en que se calculará la posición en la trayectoria.\n","\n","Las coordenadas $ x $ y $ y $ como funciones de tiempo se pueden recuperar mediante las siguientes expresiones\n","\n","$$x(t) = a(\\cos E - \\epsilon)$$\n","\n","$$y(t) = b\\sin E$$\n","\n","donde $ b = a \\sqrt {1- \\epsilon ^ 2} $ es el eje semi-menor de la órbita y la dependencia temporal implícita de la anomalía excéntrica $ E $ se calcula a través de la ecuación de Kepler.\n","\n","**Problem:**\n","\n","Para una estrellita que orbita la Tierra en una trayectoria ecuatorial con excentricidad $ \\epsilon = 0.5 $ a una distancia geoestacionaria para el eje semi-mayor, tabule las posiciones $ x $ y $ y $ dentro del plano orbital en intervalos de $ 15 $ min durante $ 5 $ horas, graficar x y y.\n","\n","**Parameters:**\n","\n","- $\\epsilon = 0.5$\n","\n","- $a = 35900$ km\n","\n","- $G = 6.67384 \\times 10^{-11}$ m$^3$ kg$^{-1}$ s$^{-2}$\n","\n","- $M_{\\oplus} = 5.972\\times 10^{24}$ kg"]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["#parametros\n","t = np.arange(0,18100,900) #5 horas = 18mil segundo cada 15min= 900 s\n","\n","epsilon = 0.5 #excentricidad\n","a = 35900000  #eje semimayor\n","G = 6.67384e-11 #contsante gravitacionnal\n","m = 5.972e24 #masa del cuerpo central\n","\n","b = a*((1-(epsilon**2))**1/2)\n","\n","M = (((G*m/(a**3))*t)**1/2)\n","\n"],"metadata":{"id":"dL3OGz_1uliS"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# E - e sen E - M\n","#M = E- e sen E\n","def funcion(E,i):\n","  y = E - (epsilon*(np.sin(E)))-(M[i])\n","  return y\n","\n","def deriv(E):\n","  y = 1 - epsilon*np.cos(E)\n","  return y"],"metadata":{"id":"Gl7CCW7V0uvS"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["E = []\n","for i in range(len(M)):\n","  e = 1\n","  xi  = 0.0\n","  cont = 0\n","  while abs(e >= 1/100) :\n","    x1 = xi - ( ( funcion(xi,i) ) / (deriv(xi) ))\n","    e = abs ((x1 - xi) / x1 )\n","    xi = x1\n","    cont += 1\n","  E.append(xi)\n","print(f\"las raices son {E} \")\n"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"raGtD46MGxwK","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1694049391000,"user_tz":300,"elapsed":334,"user":{"displayName":"SOFIA MOSCOSO ORTIZ","userId":"16663054995924911074"}},"outputId":"6d67732f-d27d-4208-e505-d02309e0a84c"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["las raices son [0.0, 7.752731678574141e-06, 1.5505463356682306e-05, 2.3258195033858516e-05, 3.10109267096368e-05, 3.876365838355116e-05, 4.651639005513566e-05, 5.426912172392429e-05, 6.202185338945109e-05, 6.977458505125005e-05, 7.752731670885523e-05, 8.528004836180066e-05, 9.303278000962033e-05, 0.0001007855116518483, 0.00010853824328801855, 0.00011629097491766511, 0.00012404370654032205, 0.00013179643815552336, 0.00013954916976280303, 0.00014730190136169515, 0.0001550546329517337] \n"]},{"output_type":"stream","name":"stderr","text":["<ipython-input-68-aee2b325368e>:8: RuntimeWarning: invalid value encountered in double_scalars\n","  e = abs ((x1 - xi) / x1 )\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["x = a*(np.cos(E) - epsilon)\n","y = b * (np.sin(E))\n","\n","plt.figure(figsize=(5,5))\n","plt.plot(x,y, \"-\" , color = \"red\" )\n","plt.xlabel(\"Posicion x\")\n","plt.ylabel(\"Posicion y\")\n","plt.title(\"Trayectoria de la estrellita\")\n","plt.grid()\n","plt.show()"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":487},"id":"nl7xrr4H08Hi","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1694049394633,"user_tz":300,"elapsed":1036,"user":{"displayName":"SOFIA MOSCOSO ORTIZ","userId":"16663054995924911074"}},"outputId":"fa4415ee-f962-4e12-e023-513f32195d6f"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["<Figure size 500x500 with 1 Axes>"],"image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"6HGBgaWysgeu"},"source":["#**2**\n","Un objeto que cae verticalmente a través del aire está sujeto a una resistencia viscosa así como a la fuerza de la gravedad. Suponga que un objeto con masa m se deja caer desde una altura s0 y que la altura del objeto después de t segundos es:\n","$$S(t)=s_0-\\frac{mg}{k}t+\\frac{m^2g}{k}t(1-e^{-kt/m})$$\n","Donde $g=32.17ft/s^2$ y $k$ representa el coeficiente de resistencia en $lbs/ft$ suponga $s_{0}=300 ft$, $m=0.25lb$, y $k=0.1lbs/ft$.\n","\n","**A** Encunetre con los 4 métodos vistos en clase y dentro de 0,01 s, el tiempo que tarda este cuarto de libra en tocar el suelo.\n","\n","**B** Compare estas cuatro soluciones repecto al numero de iteraciones y el tiempo de computom. ¿Qué podrias decir sobrte esto?\n","\n","\n","\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["g , s0 , m , k =  32.17 , 300 , 0.25 , 0.1\n","\n","def S(t):\n","  S = s0 - (m*g/k)*t + (m**2*g/k)*t*(1 -np.exp(-k*t/m))\n","  return S\n","\n","def derivada(t):\n","  derivada = (-m*g/k) + np.exp(-k*t/m)*(k*t/m - 1) + 1\n","  return derivada\n"],"metadata":{"id":"suwfJsOYv8V2"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# #Metodo de la secante\n","inicio=time.time()\n","e = 1\n","xi  = 1\n","cont = 0\n","while abs(S(xi) >= 1/100):\n","  x1 = xi - ( ( (xi - (xi -1))*S(xi) ) / ( S(xi) - S((xi-1)) ) )\n","\n","  e = abs ((x1 - xi) / x1 )\n","  xi = x1\n","  cont += 1\n","\n","final=time.time()\n","print(f\"la raiz es {xi} , el error es {e} ,con {cont} iteraciones , en un tiempo de {final-inicio}\")\n","\n","\n","\n"],"metadata":{"id":"pYxaN4WLAEKL","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1694096467218,"user_tz":300,"elapsed":199,"user":{"displayName":"SOFIA MOSCOSO ORTIZ","userId":"16663054995924911074"}},"outputId":"257f2d5b-304a-46d7-98fd-721a6b9b39f5"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["la raiz es 4.73611791382524 , el error es 0.00147495424795952 ,con 3 iteraciones , en un tiempo de 0.0003306865692138672\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# Metodo de Newton\n","inicio=time.time()\n","e = 1\n","xi  = 0.0\n","cont = 0\n","while e != 0:\n","  x1 = xi - ( ( S(xi) ) / (derivada(xi) ))\n","  e = abs ((x1 - xi) / x1 )\n","  xi = x1\n","\n","  cont += 1\n","final=time.time()\n","print(f\"la raiz es {xi} , el error es {e} ,con {cont} iteraciones, en un tiempo de {final-inicio}\")\n"],"metadata":{"id":"hIQV6Xrc_xLi","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1694096479941,"user_tz":300,"elapsed":7,"user":{"displayName":"SOFIA MOSCOSO ORTIZ","userId":"16663054995924911074"}},"outputId":"45d765ba-d2fb-4744-d8e7-973e42a74f74"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["la raiz es 4.73613913760349 , el error es 0.0 ,con 30 iteraciones, en un tiempo de 0.0005054473876953125\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["#Metodo de Biseccion\n","inicio=time.time()\n","cont = 0\n","a , b = 0 , 10\n","m= 1\n","while abs(S(m) >= 1/100):\n","  fa = S(a)\n","  fb = S(b)\n","  if fa*fb < 0:\n","    m = (a + b)/2\n","    fm = S(m)\n","    if fa*fm < 0 :\n","      a , b = a , m\n","    elif fb*fm < 0:\n","      a , b  = m , b\n","    cont += 1\n","\n","final=time.time()\n","print(f\"la raiz es {m} , con {cont} iteraciones, en un tiempo de {final-inicio}\")\n"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"yxuWpb7hQIVO","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1694096490673,"user_tz":300,"elapsed":8,"user":{"displayName":"SOFIA MOSCOSO ORTIZ","userId":"16663054995924911074"}},"outputId":"66356369-33f6-4ea2-e0e6-e232a3bf9c7c"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["la raiz es 5.0 , con 1 iteraciones, en un tiempo de 0.0003235340118408203\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["#metodo de punto fijo\n","inicio=time.time()\n","def gx(t):\n","  gx = (s0 + (m**2*g/k)*t*(1 -np.exp(-k*t/m))) * (k /m*g)\n","  return gx\n","\n","xi = 1\n","e = 1\n","cont = 0\n","while abs(e >= 1/100):\n","  x1 = (gx(xi))\n","  e = abs ((xi - x1) / xi )\n","  xi = x1\n","  cont += 1\n","\n","final=time.time()\n","print(f\"la raiz es {xi} , el error es {e} ,con {cont} iteraciones, en un tiempo de {final-inicio}\")\n","\n","## ERROR\n"],"metadata":{"id":"3ECpV-tRW7VR","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1694096500733,"user_tz":300,"elapsed":211,"user":{"displayName":"SOFIA MOSCOSO ORTIZ","userId":"16663054995924911074"}},"outputId":"6c0dc0af-a908-4eaa-bdf3-1d092ba65f70"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["la raiz es inf , el error es nan ,con 85 iteraciones, en un tiempo de 0.0034482479095458984\n"]},{"output_type":"stream","name":"stderr","text":["<ipython-input-13-1e6c1c36c12c>:4: RuntimeWarning: overflow encountered in double_scalars\n","  gx = (s0 + (m**2*g/k)*t*(1 -np.exp(-k*t/m))) * (k /m*g)\n","<ipython-input-13-1e6c1c36c